    "1. GitHubにログイン\n2. Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens → Tokens (classic)\n3. Generate new token (classic)\n4. Expiration: 任意\n5. Scope: read:user にチェック\n6. 生成されたトークンをコピー\n7. このアプリに貼り付け": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "1. Log in to GitHub\n2. Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens → Tokens (classic)\n3. Generate new token (classic)\n4.Expiration: Optional\n5. Check Scope: read:user\n6. Copy the generated token\n7. Paste into this app"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "1. GitHubにログイン\n2. Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens → Tokens (classic)\n3. Generate new token (classic)\n4. Expiration: 任意\n5. Scope: read:user にチェック\n6. 生成されたトークンをコピー\n7. このアプリに貼り付け"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "1. GitHub에 로그인\n2. Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens → Tokens (classic)\n3. Generate new token (classic)\n4. Expiration: 선택\n5. Scope: read:user 확인\n6. 생성된 토큰 복사\n7. 이 앱에 붙여넣기"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "1.登录GitHub\n2. 设置 → 开发者设置 → 个人访问令牌 → 令牌（经典）\n3.生成新的token（经典）\n4.有效期：可选\n5.检查范围：read:user\n6.复制生成的token\n7. 粘贴到此应用程序中"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "1.登入GitHub\n2. 設定 → 開發者設定 → 個人存取權令牌 → 令牌（經典）\n3.生成新的token（經典）\n4.有效期限：可選\n5.檢查範圍：read:user\n6.複製生成的token\n7. 貼上到此應用程式中"
          }
        }
      }
    },
