    "移動が多くて歩き疲れたけれど、夕方のコーヒーで復活。": {
      "comment": "Literal from lifelog/Services/AppDataStore+SampleData.swift",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "I was tired from walking so much, but the evening coffee revived me."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "移動が多くて歩き疲れたけれど、夕方のコーヒーで復活。"
