    "📋 クリップボード警告: 期間が長いと、コピーに時間がかかったり、アプリの動作が重くなる場合があります。": {
      "comment": "Literal from lifelog/Views/AIExport/AnalysisExportView.swift",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "📋 Clipboard warning: If the period is long, it may take longer to copy or the app may become slower."
